verbose_text: Food consumption was not different between the two strains of mice (data not shown), as were plasma total cholesterol (76.9 +/- 23.1 mg/dL versus 66.5 +/- 17.5 mg/dL in 9-week-old WT and P2rx7 -/- animals, respectively; n = 5) and plasma triglyceride levels (104.2 +/- 25.4 mg/dL versus 95.4 +/- 14.9 mg/dL in WT and P2rx7 -/- animals, respectively).
